text: Caj Malmberg (born 24 January 1948) is a Finnish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
